description:
The datas correspond to article entitled: &quot;Denaturing and dNTPs reagents improve SARS-CoV-2 detection via single and multiplex RT-qPCR&quot;.&nbsp; 

 The file entitle GISAID have the fasta formats for 107259 genomes from the SARS-CoV-2 GISAID database from January to December 2020. Three documents in plane tex correspond: 
sequences.fasta contain the original data. 
sequences_clean.fasta. Corresponds to genomes sequences without nucleotides undeterminateds indicates with &quot;N&quot; in previous document. 
alignment_clean.fasta. Contain the genomes sequences cleaned alingment. &nbsp; 

 The file entitle GenBank &nbsp;have the data set from 19317 &nbsp;genomes from the SARS-CoV-2 GenBank database &nbsp;from January to October 2020 and the documets have the prrevious order.

